snippet.title: NES Longplay [098] Excite Bike
snippet.description:
http://www.longplays.org

Played by: Valis77

Back in my days i dominated this game in the arcades, now im a little rusty. Anywho,this game had a remake on the wii but it still not the best compared to the original. Stage 5 just loops endessly. so theres no point in continuing a loops stage. -
